{{Infobox football club | clubname = KF Ramiz Sadiku | image = KF Ramiz Sadiku.gif| | image_size = 200px | fullname = Klub Futbollistik Ramiz Sadiku | nickname = ''Bardhë e zinjtë'' (The White & Blacks) | founded = {{Start date and years ago|df=yes|1950}} | ground = Stadiumi "Ramiz Sadikut" | capacity = 5,000 | chairman = | manager = | league = [[Liga e Parë]] | season = 2017/18 | position = 11th [[Liga e Parë]] | pattern_la1=_upperwhite|pattern_b1=_udinese1011a|pattern_ra1=_upperwhite| leftarm1=thinblackborder|body1=FFFFFF |rightarm1=thinblackborder|shorts1=FFFFFF|socks1=FFFFFF|| }} '''KF Ramiz Sadiku''' (Klubi Futbollistik Ramiz Sadiku) is a [[Association football|football]] club from [[Kosovo]] which is playing in the 2nd level (Liga 1) in Kosovo. The club have been 1 time Champions on the regional [[Kosovar Superliga]] and that was in the 1982/1983 season. It is named for [[Ramiz Sadiku]].
