'''Kepez Belediyespor''' is a [[basketball]] club based in [[Kepez, Antalya|Kepez]] - [[Antalya]], [[Turkey]] that plays in the [[Turkish Basketball League]]. They got promoted from the Second League as the runners-up in the 2006-2007 season. They finished their 2007-2008 [[Turkish Basketball League|TBL]] season in 11th spot with 12 wins.

The club is sponsored by [[Kepez, Antalya|Kepez Municipality]].

