{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Stade Jlidi Zarzis | image = | location = [[Zarzis]], [[Tunisia]] | opened = 2003 | renovated = | surface = Grass | tenants = [[Espérance Sportive de Zarzis]] | seating_capacity = 7,000
}} '''Stade Jlidi''' ({{Lang-ar|ملعب الجليدي}}) is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Zarzis]], [[Tunisia]]. It is currently used by [[football (soccer)|football]] team [[Espérance Sportive de Zarzis]]. The stadium holds 7,000 people.
