{{Infobox bandy team | team = Vostok | logo = Vostok Arsenyev logo.jpg | founded = {{start date and age|1953}} | folded = | league = [[Russian Bandy Supreme League]] | division = Group 3 | arena = [[Vostok Stadium (Arsenyev)|Vostok Stadium]] | city = [[Arsenyev]], Russia | coach = | website = {{URL|https://vostok-ars.jimdo.com/}} <!-- Home --> |pattern_he1 = |pattern_la1 = |pattern_b1 = |pattern_ra1 = |pattern_sh1 = |pattern_so1 = |leftarm1 = |body1 = |rightarm1 = |shorts1 = <!-- Away --> |pattern_he2 = |pattern_la2 = |pattern_b2 = |pattern_ra2 = |pattern_sh2 = |pattern_so2 = |leftarm2 = |body2 = |rightarm2 = |shorts2 = }} '''Vostok''' ({{lang-ru|Восток}}) is a [[bandy]] club in [[Arsenyev]], Russia. The club was founded in 1953, has earlier been playing in the [[Russian Bandy Super League]], the top-tier of Russian bandy, and now plays in [[Russian Bandy Supreme League]].<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.rusbandy.ru/club/39/|publisher= rusbandy.ru|title= «Восток» Арсеньев|language= Russian|accessdate= 20 July 2015}}</ref> The home games are played at [[Stadium Vostok]].<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.rusbandy.ru/stadium/46/|publisher= rusbandy.ru|title= Стадион «Восток», Арсеньев|language= Russian|accessdate= 20 July 2015}}</ref> The club colours are red and blue.<ref>[http://vostokbandy.ru/ Official homepage]</ref>
