'''Villingili Youth and Sports Association''' is a [[Republic of the Maldives|Maldivian]] sports club best known for its [[football (soccer)|football]] team. This club is based in [[Villingili (Malé)|Villingili]],<ref name="maldivesoccer.net" /> currently playing for top division.
